descriptionHtml:
This adds CHSBHC BBP support to the Devilmaid2 and Mandu Armour by Neo. It requires Neo's Original mod

Required mods: 
- Devilmaid2 and Mandu by Neo   ( http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/42736//?) (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/36431//?)
- A body replacer with CHSBHC BBP . 

Recommended:
========================
CHSBHC body mod and BBP -Breast and Butt Physics 
FNIS Behavior Files and Generator 4.0.2
CBBE-CHSBHC-UNP-ADEC-Human Argonian Khajiit Texture-4096
NoMaaM Breathing Idles BBB 
NoMaaM Walk BBB - inverse orientation

Installation:
1st -Devilmaid by Neo - ver Public -http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/42736//?
2nd- Mandu by Neo- http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/36431//?
Unpack the contents to your Skyrim data folder. overwrite existing file.

Console command : "help DM2 4" 


Credits and thanks: 
- Meister aka Neovinci for Devilmaid2 & Mandu by Neo 
- CHSBHC body mod and BBP by CherryHotaling  
- xp32 for UNPB REDUX PROJECT
